---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | NailTheQuote"
  description="NailTheQuote privacy policy. How we handle your data, email collection, and account information."
  currentPath="/privacy"
>
  <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p class="text-text-primary font-medium">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">The Short Version</h2>
        <p>NailTheQuote ("we," "us," or "our") is operated by High Intent Labs. NailTheQuote provides free tools for tradespeople. All calculators, templates, and estimators work without an account. If you choose to share your email or create an account, we explain exactly what we collect and why below.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">What We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-3"><strong class="text-text-primary">If you use tools without signing up:</strong> Your calculator inputs and results stay in your browser. We do not store them on our servers.</p>
        <p class="mb-3"><strong class="text-text-primary">If you enter your email:</strong> We collect your email address when you use the "Email these results to yourself" feature. If the marketing consent checkbox is checked, we add your email to our mailing list for free tool updates and tips. You can unsubscribe at any time.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-text-primary">If you create an account:</strong> We collect your email address and, optionally, your name, company name, and license number. Account data is stored securely in Supabase (our database provider) and used to save your calculations, documents, and preferences.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Email delivery:</strong> To send you calculation results, invoices, or documents you requested.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Account functionality:</strong> To save and retrieve your calculations, documents, and business profile across sessions and devices.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Marketing (opt-in only):</strong> To send free tool announcements, tips, and updates. Only if you checked the consent box. Unsubscribe link in every email.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">What We Don't Do</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>We don't sell your data to anyone.</li>
          <li>We don't share your email with third parties for their marketing.</li>
          <li>We don't use tracking cookies or advertising pixels.</li>
          <li>We don't store your calculator inputs unless you have an account and explicitly save them.</li>
          <li>We don't access your financial data from invoices or estimates — those are generated in your browser.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Local Storage</h2>
        <p>Our tools use your browser's local storage to remember your preferences, visit count, and login session. This data stays on your device and is not transmitted to our servers unless you explicitly save a calculation to your account. You can clear this data at any time through your browser settings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Cloudflare:</strong> Hosting and CDN. Cloudflare collects standard server logs. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" class="text-accent hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Supabase:</strong> Database and authentication. Stores account data and saved calculations securely. See <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy" class="text-accent hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Supabase's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Resend:</strong> Email delivery. Processes your email address to deliver results and marketing emails. See <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-accent hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Resend's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary">Google Fonts:</strong> Typography. Google may collect anonymized usage data through font requests.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Data Retention</h2>
        <p>Email addresses collected through the email capture form are retained until you unsubscribe. Account data is retained for as long as your account exists. You can delete your account and all associated data at any time by contacting us.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You can request a copy of your data, ask us to correct it, or ask us to delete it entirely. Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@nailthequote.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy@nailthequote.com</a> and we'll handle it within 7 business days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Changes</h2>
        <p>If we change this policy, we'll update this page and the "Last updated" date above. If you have an account, we may also notify you by email for significant changes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-text-primary mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Reach us at <a href="mailto:privacy@nailthequote.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">privacy@nailthequote.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
